      "comment": "DARBY SAID (4) is a patchy beginner. Latest effort finished 6th on March 4 over 330m at this track behind Perfect Liam beaten 5 lengths (19.43) in a Grade 5. Looks a leading chance and expected to go close. INDECISION (1) turned in a moderate performance last time when seventh at this track over 330m behind Sonali (20.19) in a Grade 5. Placed at his previous run. Should be in this for a long way. BLUE JEZEBEL (8) missed the frame and was safely held latest finishing 6th at this track following on from a third place finish (19.56) there the start prior. Worth another chance. PA KETTLE (3) cannot be left out despite coming off a short break.",
